snippet.title: Depp 'painted with blood of severed finger after Ecstasy and vodka binge'
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp has been giving evidence in the third day of his libel case against the publisher of The Sun.

The hearing was shown images of scrawling on a mirror said to have been done after a violent argument between Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard.

The Hollywood star is suing the newspaper over claims he was violent towards Heard.
